IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User julian.grove@gmail.com
PassCmd "~/.nix-profile/bin/gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.gmailpass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/inbox

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :gmail-local:drafts
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:sent
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :gmail-local:trash
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gmail-all
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:all
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-all

IMAPAccount exchange
Host outlook.office365.com
User juliang@uchicago.edu
PassCmd "~/.nix-profile/bin/gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.exchangepass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore exchange-remote
Account exchange

MaildirStore exchange-local
Path ~/.mail/exchange/
Inbox ~/.mail/exchange/inbox

Channel exchange-inbox
Master :exchange-remote:
Slave :exchange-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel exchange-sent
Master :exchange-remote:"Sent Items"
Slave :exchange-local:sent
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel exchange-trash
Master :exchange-remote:"Deleted Items"
Slave :exchange-local:trash
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Group exchange
Channel exchange-inbox
Channel exchange-sent
Channel exchange-trash